@node "future" "Cookie.guide/Future"
Any ideas ?
Send them to @{"me" link "author" }!

For those of you who have really read this document to its end,
I provide a special service ;-)
If you like this module very much, and would like to hear about
updates or other modules, write me an email. I will store your
email address in a list; and everytime I update this module or
I upload another module to the aminet I will send you an email
alarming you to download the new stuff from aminet.
I promise that I won't use the collected email addresses to send
you any other unwanted material. I won't send you the archives
directly per email, so you can choose yourself what you download.
Again a short email is enough to stop this service.
I won't give your address to others.
@endnode


